text.tspan: Default state of the keyboard is lower case,
Key shows the Shift icon an is in a normal state.
Single press of the shift key toggles the keys to
uppercase and that state is released when another
Key is styled in a pressed state.
Long press of the shift key activates Caps-Lock,
which is de-activated by another long press.
Key shows caps-lock icon and is styled in a
selected state to indicate said mode.
